data.description: Be the proud owner of this delightful property located in a desirable gated community. You will love the stone accents on its facade, RV gate and RV parking. Be greeted by an expansive open and split floor plan featuring sleek tile floors and a calming color palette. Spacious great room is perfect for gatherings. Lovely kitchen dazzles with neutral cabinets, SS appliances, a large pantry, tile backsplash, granite counters, and a center island with a breakfast bar. Retreat to the primary bedroom for relaxation with an ensuite showcasing dual sinks, a soaking tub, and a walk-in closet. A versatile den is ideal for an office or media center. Entertain your guest in your very own backyard oasis featuring covered patio, soft grass, ample seating areas and a gorgeous newly built salt water pool
